---
// EN / JA language switch. Interaction is wired up in BaseLayout's script.
---

<span class="lang" role="group" aria-label="Language">
    <button type="button" data-lang="en" aria-pressed="true">EN</button><span class="sep">/</span><button
        type="button"
        data-lang="ja"
        aria-pressed="false">JA</button
    >
</span>
